      "Text": "Security update for the Linux Kernel (Live Patch 78 for SUSE Linux Enterprise 12 SP5)",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "\nThis update for the SUSE Linux Enterprise kernel 4.12.14-122.296 fixes one security issue\n\nThe following security issue was fixed:\n\n- CVE-2026-31431: crypto: algif_aead - Revert to operating out-of-place (bsc#1263689).\n",
